title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update  -  City Update 1 available and more
description:
In this video we look at the new which was released about MSFS today at Gamescom. CU 1 was released where CU stand for city update. The first city update will add photogrammetry content to cities located in Germany. In addition to this local  legend 6 was released and some more information was shared about the 40th anniversary edition which is scheduled to be released in November.
